Package: btrfscue
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Advanced data recovery tool for the BTRFS filesystem.
 btrfscue is designed to restore data
 - from disk images of faulty storage devices.
 - even when all superblocks are missing/were overwritten.
 - of recently deleted files.
